data.description: Well maintained 3 bedroom ranch style home that is ready for new owners. There's a LOT to get excited about with this 3 bed 1 bath home. Nice sized bedrooms with conveniently located full bathroom. Eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops and space saving built-in microwave. A formal dining room for larger gatherings, plus a living room with newer LVT plank flooring and cozy wood burning fireplace. Great fenced-in backyard with access to 2 car garage with long lasting metal roof. New roof on the house in 2023. Best of all... this home is very energy efficient! Brand NEW 96% high efficiency "Heil" furnace installed Dec 2023. Complete solar energy system owned and included. 13 solar panels on the garage roof supply the house with power and battery back-up with a quality Generac electric system. This great system is owned, not leased. Meaning no solar payments, just energy savings for years to come!
